The '''Nuun''' were members of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Warrior caste]] which were designated to become the physical incarnation of the [[Hunters]]. They wore advanced versions of the [[Cloak of Nuun]], and were better trained than most other Hunters. Only one in a thousand Warriors would be designated a Nuun.

